🏠 House Price Prediction using Machine Learning

# Project Overview
This project predicts house prices based on various features such as area, location, condition, and other property-related factors using Machine Learning techniques.
# Dataset
- Dataset used: Ames Housing Dataset
- Features include:
  - Lot Area
  - Overall Condition
  - Year Built
  - Basement Area
  - Exterior Type
# Technologies Used
- Python
- Pandas
- NumPy
- Scikit-learn
# Model Used
- Linear Regression
# Steps Performed
1. Data Cleaning  
2. Handling Missing Values  
3. Feature Encoding  
4. Feature Scaling  
5. Model Training  
6. Model Evaluation  
# Results
- Model: Linear Regression
- R² Score: 0.37
- Mean Absolute Error:30746.8

# Key Learnings
- Importance of feature selection  
- Handling missing data  
- Feature scaling techniques  
- Model evaluation using regression metrics  
